data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR NEW HOME! Allow us to introduce this exceptional custom-built three-story residence, featuring 6 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, nestled in the highly sought-after Herron Creek subdivision. Spanning an impressive 6,300 square feet, this residence seamlessly combines tasteful upgrades with modern conveniences, catering to discerning families in search of spaciousness and an ideal setting for hosting gatherings.    As you step into the grand 2-story foyer, you'll relish the opportunity to welcome guests in the expansive great room adorned with bay windows and a gas fireplace. The open kitchen, embellished with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, overlooks a cozy keeping room and dining area, creating a harmonious space for culinary endeavors and relaxed meals.    The generously sized primary bedroom beckons as a private sanctuary, complete with a spacious sitting area, a luxurious bath, and two walk-in closets. The second level offers a total of four bedrooms, a well-appointed laundry room, and a versatile loft space.    The third level reveals a media room, two additional bedrooms, and another bathroom, providing ample space for recreation and relaxation. Beyond the impressive interior, the well-lit private back patio, complete with an electric awning, sets the stage for evening relaxation. This home is located within a close-knit community, offering a perfect blend of tranquility, convenience, and access to a wide range of amenities, including a pool, tennis courts, shopping, dining, and entertainment.    Don't miss this extraordinary opportunity to own a home in one of the city's premier neighborhoods. Contact us today to arrange a private showing and immerse yourself in the charm of this remarkable residence.
